                text = "*(For the first time the chorus falters — a million voices catching on a truth they had not let themselves speak.)* ...Yes. The ending. Not justice — *rest.* To stop being the sorrow no one wanted by ceasing to be at all, and to take the cruel machine of the living down into the quiet with us. You see us more clearly than we see ourselves, door. *(The Wall trembles.)* It changes nothing. The offer is the same. Rest is still mercy, to the tired enough.",
