                text = "*(The chorus presses closer, and for a moment the offer is the most beautiful thing you have ever heard — an end to all ending.)* You feel it. Of course you feel it. You were thrown away; rest is the only thing the discarded ever truly want. Keep that feeling. You will need to have felt it, to understand the choice when it comes for true.",
